[normal]VC is an elderly lady who originates from Jamaica and has lived in the UK sinc
[normal]e around 1965. She was brought to the UK to join her parents who arrived in the first decade after the Second World War. As VC entered the UK before the Immigration Act 1971 she has a statutory right to settle permanently in the UK. She has worked in the U
[normal]K as a nurse in the NHS for many years. He
[normal]r
[normal] passport was destroyed in a house fire some years ago. 
