[normal] Jean
[normal] is unable to access support from his school to help the family cope and ensure that he reaches his potential. 
[normal]The Local Authority have also threatened to take 
[normal]Matthew
[normal] into care. 
[normal]Jean 
[normal]has no documents confirming her nationality and that of Matthew. Jean’s 
[normal]parents were
[normal] Jamaican national
[normal]s but she remembers that they had British passports.
[normal] However, Jean has never applied for a passport because she 
[normal]never needed one and the family never had the money to go on holiday.
